#. module: sale_lazada
#: model:mail.template,body_html:sale_lazada.order_sync_failure
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<div>\n"
"                <p>The synchronization of the Lazada order with reference <t "
"t-out=\"ctx.get('lazada_order_ref') or ''\">REF</t> encountered an error and "
"was not completed.</p>\n"
"                <p>Unless the order is cancelled in Lazada, no other "
"synchronization will be attempted.</p>\n"
"                <p>To schedule a new synchronization attempt, proceed as "
"follows:\n"
"                    </p><ol>\n"
"                        <li>Enter the Developer Tools.</li>\n"
"                        <li>Open the form of the Lazada Shop on which the "
"order was placed.</li>\n"
"                        <li>Navigate to the Order Follow-up tab.</li>\n"
"                        <li>Set a date for <em>Last Order Synchronization "
"Date</em> that is anterior to the last status update of the order.</li>\n"
"                        <li>Save the changes and click on the <em>SYNC "
"ORDERS</em> button.</li>\n"
"                    </ol>\n"
"                \n"
"                <p>If the problem persists, contact <a href=\"https://"
"www.odoo.com/help/\">Odoo support</a>.</p>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div>\n"
"                <p>Sinkronisasi pesanan Lazada dengan referensi <t t-"
"out=\"ctx.get('lazada_order_ref') or ''\">REF</t> mengalami kesalahan dan "
"tidak selesai.</p>\n"
"                <p>Upaya sinkronisasi tidak akan dijalankan lagi kecuali "
"pesanan dibatalkan di Lazada.</p>\n"
"                <p>Untuk menjadwalkan upaya sinkronisasi baru, lakukan "
"langkah berikut:\n"
"                   </p><ol> \n"
"                       <li> Masuk ke Developer Tools.</li>\n"
"                        <li>Buka halaman Toko Lazada tempat pesanan tersebut "
"dibuat.</li>\n"
"                        <li>Buka tab Order Follow-up.</li>\n"
"                        <li>Atur tanggal untuk <em>Last Order "
"Synchronization Date</em> (Tanggal Sinktonisasi Pesanan Terakhir) yang lebih "
"awal dari pembaruan status terakhir pesanan.</li>\n"
"                        <li>Simpan perubahan dan klik tombol <em>SYNC "
"ORDERS\"</em> (SINKRONKAN PESANAN).</li>\n"
"                    </ol>\n"
"                \n"
"               <p> Jika masalah berlanjut, hubungi <a href=\"https://"
"www.odoo.com/help/\">dukungan Odoo</a>.</p>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "

